      • getParametricRanges

        List<FieldRanges> getParametricRanges(Collection<String> fieldNames,
                                      Collection<ResourceName> indexes,
                                      String ranges,
                                      GetParametricRangesRequestBuilder params)
                               throws HodErrorException
        Query parametric ranges for the fieldNames using a token proxy provided by a TokenProxyService
        Parameters:
        fieldNames - A list of field names to return ranges for
        indexes - The indexes to get ranges from
        ranges - String specifying the ranges to query for
        params - Additional parameters to be sent as part of the request
        Returns:
        A list of field names with their parametric ranges
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - If a TokenProxyService has not been defined
        HodAuthenticationFailedException - If the token associated with the token proxy has expired
        HodErrorException
